學科別分類



中文摘要
都市空間猶如一篇完整的文章，由一個個的單字詞彙組合而成為句子，再藉由文法與文句的安排構築而成。舊市區環境的成長與演變有其獨特的背景與意義，相對於現代化街廓外圍的人造環境與單一機能的使用分區，街廓內既有的生活環境更顯得親切與具生命力，具備歷史環境意義與文化價值的街巷空間，並非過去生活記憶的「遺跡」，而是居民生活場域的的延伸，隨著時間的演變，留存老街、港道等紋理以及不同型態與文化發展形成特有的生活空間氛圍，在未完全開發的街廓中，仍具備保有地方生活感並且與舊市區再發展的機會。五條港地區從過去因應生活環境需求有機成長而成的聚落與商港大街，演變到今日的棋盤格式街廓配置，空間模式有相當大的劇烈變動，但隱含其間的常民生活文化，仍舊依循著原來的秩序繼續留存，在不斷變動的都市環境中，除了提昇現代化生活機能之外，在地特色的保存、居民地區意識的提昇與參與需要與之並重，更是舊市區再生的重要議題。 本研究成果如下：1. 歷史環境街巷空間的維持沿街建築物(私領域)的增建與改建，是反應歷史性環境特質的街巷風貌與尺度的同時，必須面對的重要問題之一，本研究從延續歷史性街巷紋理以及調整管制建築物量體的角度，提出讓改建後建築物能夠反應出歷史性街巷環境特質的管制方式，並藉由探討其對於建築物內部空間(私有發展權)影響的討論，來達到建物改建的合理性、改善居住環境品質以及反應歷史性環境特質的目的 2. 居民參與環境改造議題討論的意義本研究透過一連串老街營造相關議題的座談、活動舉辦、案例參訪、與問捲訪談，呈現現階段老街居民的環境意識，對本研究所提出的量體管制方式的討論結果，以及居民參與環境改造議題的正面意義。「居民參與」並不等於完全要居民來做設計，許多參與的概念是期望「藉由居民參與設計發展的決策，縮小與設計者間認知的差距」，但另外一個層面，是藉由共同對於在地環境問題的關心，培養出社區意識。進而轉為社區依附心理與認同感，主動關心參與社區事務，提昇充實社區的體質與內涵，這一層的意涵才是其真正的意義。


英文摘要
The urban space just like a complete article, combined by the grammar and the sentence construction that becomes the sentence by each one individual character glossary. The old urban district environment has unique background and the significance meaning of its evolution. In opposite in the modernized district with artificial environment and the single function zoning, the living environment has appears kind and a vitality in it. The streets and alleys space with historical significance and cultural value, is not only means the “the vestige” of memory, but the extending part of inhabitant living culture. Along with the time evolution, preserves historical texture which as well as the different state and the cultural development forms the unique life space atmosphere, such as street and port. and so on the textures, still holds the place life feeling and the opportunity to relive the old urban district. The Five-Harbor District, the past the settlement and the commercial harbor avenue, growth according the living conditions, has a quite big change to spatial pattern evolves checkerboard form street today. The native living culture that conceals in this environment, is still preserve relied on the original regulation. Besides the promotion modernization vital function, native characteristic preservation, the populated country, consciousness promotion and the participation needs, are the important issues to historical district preservation, in the changing urban environment This research results are as follows （1）Historical streets and alleys space maintenanceTo responded the special characteristic and texture of historical environment is one of important questions, when additional construction and the rebuilding of the building (private domain) a long the street. This research discuss from the aspects of extension historical streets texture and the mass control of building renovation. Proposed some rules of mass control of building which respond the special characteristic of historical environment, and regarding the affects of interior space using (which mean private development. To achieve the goal of the rational and improving living quality of building rebuilds, as well as response the special characteristics of historical environment.   （2）The significance of inhabitant participates in the environment transformation subject discussion    This research presents the inhabitant's opinions, which have environmental awareness for the time, of the rules of mass control of building and the social significance of inhabitant participates in the environment transformation subject discussion, though the a series of activities including old street symposium, the activity conducts, the case visits, and the questionnaire interview.“The inhabitant participation” is not equal to wants the inhabitant to make the design completely, There are many participation concepts expected by the way of the decision-making participating process to reduction the cognition disparity between inhabitant and designer. On the other sides, it can raise the community sense and turn into the community attachment and sympathy by caring the native environment issue together. Then participate the community business on own initiative to promotion community's internal. This it’s the truly significance.


